                <head>28. Editorial Note</head>
                <p>On January 18, 1962, Chairman of the Joint Chiefs of Staff General Lemnitzer,
                    transmitted to Secretary <persName corresp="#p_MNRS1">McNamara</persName>,
                    CM-491-62, a four-paragraph memorandum on the Vietnamese command problem. For
                    text of this memorandum, see <hi rend="italic">United States-Vietnam Relations,
                        1945-1967</hi>, Book 12, pages 440-441.</p>
            </div>
